name: A.P. #701 – dark fruits
description: This image is an animation still of the interactive audiovisual installation „Anima Perplexa“. A weightless form, which unfurls freely in the space and fluidly transforms into geometric or amorphous entities. Created with Max MSP Jitter. Resolution 3840 × 2400px. Artist: Michel Winterberg, 2021, https://michelwintrberg.ch
